{"tid":1523271,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不割蓆！重點係黑警恐襲","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:02:43.000Z","uid":139282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0ad70d715049fd34f128320664e5374dc02868cc","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"今日呢單同元朗恐襲一樣<br />\n重點唔係手足做錯決定咩咩咩<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會對平民進行無差別襲擊 係恐怖襲擊</span>！<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都好心痛 但<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好幫手帶割蓆風</span><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">清洗大原則：<br />\n有咩用咩，唔好限死自己去搵某種物資嚟洗</span><br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液，用水開搽落皮膚到捽都可以，唔傷皮膚"},{"pid":"223abba61f72a64404c176e604f2be36bbe1c5cf","tid":1523271,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57abcdcf5da8bf3f7a926c74512c725ddfde236f","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"黑警無差別襲擊平民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb9c2d69ed28a44ee31cbde00583bedabc04d16","tid":1523271,"uid":117819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"香港警察大型無差別恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"8a2b1449aece65f396515b82a1a068c86d1345fd","tid":1523271,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！"},{"pid":"cbfa82c3b4dae0a222c83ca2df3da86e43af254f","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"手足做法唔完美 可改善<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">恐襲絕對零容忍</span>"},{"pid":"4f0f900c57f0929f2e25975b3f799369f5010a85","tid":1523271,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c71def9372f718db7aa3858cbc577a3df101d5a","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"太子旺角恐襲呀<br />\n<br />\n另一邊又開真槍喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53cac94163b2d572b8ffadb8cb9a90ab0009ac4","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"冇宣佈戒嚴都可以戒嚴 屌你老母"},{"pid":"500af196a3856c27b4df828053d1a16fe2820939","tid":1523271,"uid":18223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"756d813904615dab41776d637aba378858cf9e64","tid":1523271,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<